comments: Durant (PHX) is firming up over his left leg in Collins' (SAS) path, and the contact during the screen is marginal.
Collins (SAS) contests Booker's (PHX) jump shot and the contact after the release, and follow-through, is marginal.
Booker (PHX) extends both hands forward into Collins (SAS) and delivers contact that affects his FOM off-ball.
Sochan (SAS) applies his forearm to Durant's (PHX) side and immediately removes his forearm as Durant begins his upward shooting motion.
Gordon (PHX) places his hand momentarily on Vassell's (SAS) hip, and immediately removes his hand as marginal contact occurs on the perimeter.
Allen (PHX) makes contact with the ball as he defends Vassell's (SAS) jump shot attempt.
Collins (SAS) moves laterally into Booker's (PHX) path and initiates body to body contact that affects his driving shot attempt.
Collins (SAS) brings his hands toward Booker (PHX) and marginal contact occurs as Collins releases away to roll.
Gordon (PHX) is moving alongside Johnson's (SAS) path and absorbs the marginal body contact that occurs during Johnson's drive.
Johnson (SAS) brings his forearm towards Booker's (PHX) front and marginal contact occurs during the drive.
Collins (SAS) contests Durant's (PHX) jump shot attempt and avoids making contact with his left arm.
Sochan (SAS) and O'Neale (PHX) briefly engage and disengage as they position themselves for the rebound.
Johnson (SAS) legally contests Booker's (PHX) jump shot attempt.
O'Neale (PHX) briefly grasps Vassell's (SAS) arm, and marginal contact occurs as the long rebound bounces away from their matchup.
